@* The BASE component. @inherits takes a component CLASS, and a .razor file IS one -- so a base
   written as a sibling .razor is the form this compiler can actually resolve (decision 136). Its
   MARKUP is irrelevant here: a derived component overrides BuildRenderTree, so only the members
   below are inherited. *@

@code {
    protected int count = 0;
    protected void Inc() { count++; }
}
